Package in2011.http

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Message
    The part of an HTTP message before the message body.
    RequestMessage
    The part of an HTTP request message before the message body (if any).
    ResponseMessage
    The part of an HTTP response message before the message body (if any).
    StatusCodes
    The HTTP status codes.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EmptyMessageException
    This exception is thrown when a byte sequence is expected to contain an HTTP message but the end of the sequence is reached before any message is found.
    MessageFormatException
    This exception is thrown when a byte sequence is expected to contain an HTTP message but is found not to comply with the format specified in RFC 2616.
    UnexpectedEndOfSequenceException
    This exception is thrown when the end of a byte sequence is reached unexpectedly.
